Package nusri.fyp.demo.roboflow.data.request

Class WorkflowsBlocksDescriptionRequest

java.lang.Object
nusri.fyp.demo.roboflow.data.RoboflowRequestData
nusri.fyp.demo.roboflow.data.request.WorkflowsBlocksDescriptionRequest
public class WorkflowsBlocksDescriptionRequest extends RoboflowRequestData
Represents a request to describe blocks within a workflow.
This request is used to fetch the description of blocks that are part of a workflow, including dynamic block definitions and the execution engine version.
